description: The Go-Soccer club was formed by Daiku Kenzaburou on a whim, without his knowing that it really was a sport. Started as a general do-nothing club, the level of play shoots up once MVPs http://anidb.net/ch29036 [Sakurai Makoto] and http://anidb.net/ch29041 [Takasaski-sensei] get in on the act.
name: Igo Soccer Bu
